  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00001",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "安学海上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00002",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "身受皇恩，为县令，秉正忠心。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00003",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "为官忠义报君王，不合上意起祸殃。黄河决口洪水涨，难免他人道短长。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00004",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "下官，安学海。家住京都。蒙圣恩钦受淮阳县知县，自到任以来，处事秉公，军民信仰。只因总漕谈大人寿辰之日，是我不会应酬，未送礼物，因此得罪总漕，恰巧黄河决口，惟恐难免有失于检查之罪。我也曾命管家华忠到上衙打听消息，去了两日不见回来，好不烦闷人也。",
      "text_length": 121
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00005",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "夫人出堂。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00006",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "佟夫人、丫鬟同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00007",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "夫受皇家禄，妻沾雨露恩。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00008",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "夫人请坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00009",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "老爷请坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00010",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "咳。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00011",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "老爷为何长叹？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00012",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "总漕寿辰，下官未曾送礼，不想得罪于他。今黄河决口，惟恐总漕借此机会，以失于检查为名，陷害于我。曾命华忠到上衙打听，两日未回，心中烦闷，故而长叹。",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00013",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "老爷不必忧虑，吉人自有天相。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00014",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "走哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00015",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00016",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "都只为我老爷心忠性耿，少奉敬谈大人惹下祸凶。黄河涨奏老爷公款侵用，要拿问我主人尅扣考程。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00017",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "可恼呀，可恼！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00018",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "呀呸！命你去打听消息，今日才回；进得门来，未叙长短，连道可恼，敢与你老爷生气么？",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00019",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老奴怎敢与老爷生气。老奴曾劝过老爷：上司原要应酬，老爷要做清官，正直无私，少得一份寿礼送那谈大人。恰巧黄河决口，谈大人奏老爷侵吞公款，尅扣钱粮，罚老爷六千两银子，可免无罪；要没有银子，就要将老爷拿问了。",
      "text_length": 101
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00020",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00021",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "安学海气坐椅。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00022",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人",
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老爷醒来！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00023",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "听他言不由人神魂不定，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00024",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00025",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "这件事我只得自怨自身。到如今无别法听天由命，",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00026",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "劝老爷免忧愁商议而行。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00027",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "老爷不必愁恼，大家商量个主意才好。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00028",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "遭此不白冤枉，我倒无有主意了。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00029",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老爷总要筹备六千两银子才好。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00030",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "你老爷到任以来，不贪民财，两袖清风，你是知道的，我哪有六千两银子拿得出来？",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00031",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "事到如今，并无别法，只好将老爷在京都的房屋变卖银两，打点上司，不知老爷意下如何？",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00032",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "就是变卖房产，此处离京都路远，谁能即去办得此事？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00033",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "就请老爷与少爷写封书信说明此事，老奴愿去走这一遭。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00034",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "你这大年纪，如何受得这场辛苦？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00035",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "既是如此，老管家你就收拾去罢。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00036",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00037",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00038",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "夫人浓墨！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00039",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄顶板",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "老华忠可算得忠义大，远途辛苦还要亏他。手提羊毫两泪洒，字谕我儿悉根芽：父在任所命运差，黄河水涨漫无涯。上司参奏难辩答，索银六千将父罚。我的儿将房产速行变化，变卖银两交与管家。写罢了书信划花押，快唤华忠付托他。",
      "text_length": 104
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00040",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠背包自下场门上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00041",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "收拾包裹身背定，老奴就此要登程。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00042",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "我今付你这书信，劳你年迈受劳辛。一路之上须谨慎，见了我儿详细云。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00043",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老爷不必细叮咛，我受厚恩当尽心。拜辞老爷与夫人，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00044",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠走。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00045",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "管家转来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00046",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "唤回老奴为何因？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00047",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老爷有何吩咐？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00048",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，管家呀！此番进京变卖房产，须要及早回来；若是迟误，恐怕你老爷要吃苦了。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00049",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老爷呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00050",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老爷请把心放定，老奴星夜赶途程。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00051",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠下。安学海望，哭。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00052",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "华忠，管家呀！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00053",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "安学海"
      ],
      "text": "华忠上路泪难忍，不由下官挂在心。但愿早来事安稳，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00054",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "佟夫人"
      ],
      "text": "且免愁烦听好音。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00055",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "安学海、佟夫人同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00056",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00057",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "迈开大步往前行，不顾高低路不平。心急懒观路旁景，不分昼夜奔京城。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00058",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00059",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "褚一官上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00060",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "奉了岳父命，四路谢宾朋。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00061",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "俺，褚一官。奉了岳父之命，四路拜谢亲友。俱已谢毕，回庄便了。正是：",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00062",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "侠义门前三千事，待客还须半子劳。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00063",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "褚一官下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00064",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00065",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "早行晚宿奔途程，盘费用尽无计行。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00066",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "老汉行了旬日，银钱用尽，这便怎么处？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00067",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠望。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00068",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "看那边来了一人，好像我那妹丈褚一官，待我向前看来。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00069",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖水底鱼〗。褚一官上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00070",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "你可是我妹丈？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00071",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "原来是舅兄。久违了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00072",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "妹丈一向可好，为何到此？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00073",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "舅兄有所不知，你我离别日久，不幸你令妹亡故，因为相隔路远，一时难与舅兄送信。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00074",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "我妹亡故了？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00075",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00076",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀。贤妹呀！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00077",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠哭。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00078",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "吓，妹丈，你在此作甚？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00079",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "舅兄不知。此处有廿八棵红柳村，有一邓九公，将我招赘为婿。今日幸会舅兄，请到庄上盘桓几日。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00080",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "我有要事在身，还要赶路。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00081",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "何事如此紧急？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00082",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "只因黄河决口，总槽将我老爷参奏，罚银六千两，我家老爷为官清正，不取民财，任所没有许多银两，命我进京变卖房产，方可赎罪，故而要急急赶路。",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00083",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "既有要事，不敢强留，改日再会。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00084",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "褚一官、华忠分走。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00085",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "吓，妹丈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00086",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "舅兄？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00087",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "我盘费用尽，你有现成银两，请借我使用？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00088",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "这有散碎银两，不知够用否？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00089",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华忠"
      ],
      "text": "足以够用，我就去了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00090",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华忠下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00091",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "text": "俺回庄便了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02012038_e00092",
      "play_id": "02012038",
      "scene_id": "02012038_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "褚一官下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
